{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_01","textHome":"过去的我，和编辑没什么缘分……所以，@我许下愿望「能够遇见一个能认同，@并珍视我作品的编辑」。我想要的并不是@才能……而是能够出世的机会。因为我相信，@我的故事能够触动读者的心。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":13.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":401200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":401200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":401200,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_18","textHome":"既然有推理小说，那么也有拒绝推理的@「反推理小说」。作家，在某种意义上@也是发明家。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_19","textHome":"我感觉我的力量在增加……这样子就@渐渐地超过我的对手了……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_20","textHome":"嗯，我现在大脑很清楚……！看来要有@新的灵感了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_21","textHome":"人们在写小说的时候……首先会想从哪里@开始才好。不过，最重要其实是@“你想写什么？”这样的想法。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_22","textHome":"灵感，是飘忽不定的东西。不仔细寻找的话@是找不到的。要是能发现的话，就要靠记忆@或是笔记好好保存下来，必要的时候@就能拿出来使用。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_23","textHome":"在构思故事的时候，首先考虑框架比较好。@该怎么样开始，怎么样展开，怎么样结束…@然后再用脑中的灵感去对应比较，@这样子就能有一个整体的构造了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_24","textHome":"……从这开始……从这开始的展开……嗯？@啊，你来啦。我？我还在写我的原稿。嗯，@现在……正好有些停不下来……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_25","textHome":"早上好…我，昨天做梦也在写稿子…但是，@还是想不到该写什么…明明之前@写得还挺顺的……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":401200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":401200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":300}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_26","textHome":"稿子没有预想中那么顺利……不过，饥饿@却率先无情地侵袭了过来……所以，@还是先去吃个午饭吧，"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_27","textHome":"刚刚，我有了个新想法！所以，我要赶紧整理@一下才行……！在晚饭前把这些做完吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_03","textHome":"没想到我刚刚遇见的是旧书店的孩子……@这就是作家的缘分吧……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_28","textHome":"呜～嗯……啊，你要是困了的话，就先睡吧。@我再写一点就睡。写到一半停下来的话，@我可睡不安稳的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_29","textHome":"不行……写不下去了……那么就去购物吧！@我要去买喜欢的东西了。所以，@做好充足准备吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_30","textHome":"我所走的道路，自然就是我自己的故事。@所以，我会作为作家，不断创作下去。@那么，前进吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_31","textHome":"嗯，要和我战斗的话……就不用考虑@手下留情了。因为我会看穿@你的每个动作的……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_32","textHome":"我想我已经习惯团体战了。只要配合默契，@攻击目标明确，就一定能看到胜机……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_33","textHome":"和美，我觉得她适合穿有活力，可爱的衣服。@她像个天真无邪的孩子……只有我@这么觉得吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":300}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_34","textHome":"我的原则就是食材越便宜越好。这样不好吗？@钱和生命都是需要奔波的！@所以……这才不是什么小气呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_35","textHome":"在翌桧市，任何人都有可能变成魔女……@而神滨市又是不一样的状况。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_36","textHome":"魔女会按一定的规律去袭击人们……所以，@在寻找魔女的时候，根据这一点反推@去阻止魔女也是方法的一种。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_37","textHome":"我在写稿的时候是用的电脑，@如果没有电脑的话，我就成为不了作家了吧。@钢笔……随身携带就会很帅气不是吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_04","textHome":"我在这个城市人生地不熟……@真是帮了我大忙了……总之谢谢你。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_38","textHome":"在写作遇到瓶颈的时候，我就会去做料理。@我做过热狗、意面沙拉、还有华夫饼。@才不是在说笑呢……虽然我很有幽默天赋。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_39","textHome":"不管是料理还是购物，目的都是缓解压力。@心中焦躁不安的话，思考也会受到阻碍。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_40","textHome":"自己创作的作品，我肯定会当做宝物来对待。@所以，那些胡乱对待我作品的人，@我实在是无法原谅……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_41","textHome":"诶？和美的头发？嗯，确实是我和薰剪的……@实际上我们也是第一次……@所以，剪得稍微有点乱……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":300}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_42","textHome":"那么……第一行就是……"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_43","textHome":"做得还不错。"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_44","textHome":"暂时能放下笔了。"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_45","textHome":"预想中的结局。"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_46","textHome":"理所当然的结局。"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_63","textHome":"接下来，就用我的胜利来结束吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_05","textHome":"快一点……要赶在那个魔女带来@更大的灾难之前！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_64","textHome":"涌出来了……从我灰色的脑细胞！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_65","textHome":"一口气写完吧！"}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_66","textHome":"那么，这样就完结了……X档案！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":400}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_02","textHome":"稍等一下……这里……还是不对啊……啊，@对不起。刚刚小说突然有了新的想法。@我叫御崎海香。很高兴认识你。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_13","textHome":"这是……嗯……翻开下一页的感觉呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_14","textHome":"终于到了这里……到这里就算是@打上一个句号了呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_15","textHome":"在这前方，有什么在等待着我呢……@那么，走吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_16","textHome":"小说有着各种类型。比如推理小说。重要的@就是让读者惊讶的叙事手法，@还有其中包含的逻辑。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4012_00_17","textHome":"推理小说里，也有以「本格派」为正统，@分以各种各样的类别。这里就说来话长了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":401200,"motion":200}]}]},"version":3}